South Africans were left in stitches over a viral video demonstrating the 'power of Woolworths water'.
DJ Fresh shared a video on Twitter showing three young men drastically changing their accent after drinking water that was purchased at the store. The video went viral with over 4000 retweets and 9500 favourites at the time of publishing.



